{"id":4226,"date":"2025-06-16T16:44:09","date_gmt":"2025-06-16T09:44:09","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=4226"},"modified":"2025-06-16T16:44:09","modified_gmt":"2025-06-16T09:44:09","slug":"cach-chon-kem-chong-nang-cho-cac-loai-da","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/thong-tin-nganh\/cach-chon-kem-chong-nang-cho-cac-loai-da\/","title":{"rendered":"C\u00e1ch ch\u1ecdn kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng cho c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i da"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Trong v\u00f4 v\u00e0n d\u00f2ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng hi\u1ec7n nay, vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm ra <\/span><\/i><b><i>kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng cho c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i da<\/i><\/b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n. M\u1ed7i lo\u1ea1i da l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng ri\u00eang v\u1edbi c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n trong kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng. V\u1eady l\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn da b\u1ecb k\u00edch \u1ee9ng ho\u1eb7c gi\u1ea3m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7? H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u c\u00e1ch nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft v\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng cho c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i da m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, an to\u00e0n v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"kem-chong-nang-co-tac-dung-gi-doi-voi-lan-da\"><\/span><b>Kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng g\u00ec \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi l\u00e0n da?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1edbp m\u00e0ng che ch\u1eafn, kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 nh\u01b0 \u201ct\u1ea5m khi\u00ean\u201d gi\u00fap da tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi c\u00e1c t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c t\u1eeb \u00e1nh n\u1eafng m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 tia UV (tia c\u1ef1c t\u00edm). Trong s\u1ed1 ba lo\u1ea1i tia UV, g\u1ed3m UVA, UVB v\u00e0 UVC th\u00ec ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 UVA v\u00e0 UVB l\u00e0 xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qua t\u1ea7ng ozone v\u00e0 g\u00e2y \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0n da.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tia UVA l\u00e0 \u201cth\u1ee7 ph\u1ea1m\u201d ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh l\u00e3o h\u00f3a da, c\u00f2n tia UVB l\u00e0m da b\u1ecfng r\u00e1t, ch\u00e1y n\u1eafng v\u00e0 t\u0103ng nguy c\u01a1 t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng. V\u1ec1 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i, vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean v\u1edbi UV m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u00f2n l\u00e0m t\u0103ng nguy c\u01a1 ung th\u01b0 da.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4227\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4227\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4227\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/75-1.webp\" alt=\"Kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng g\u00ec \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi l\u00e0n da\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/75-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/75-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/75-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/75-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4227\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng g\u00ec \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi l\u00e0n da<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, ch\u1ecdn kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n kh\u1ecfi c\u1ea3 UVA v\u00e0 UVB l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n g\u00ecn gi\u1eef l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"lam-sao-de-chon-kem-chong-nang-phu-hop-voi-tung-loai-da\"><\/span><b>L\u00e0m sao \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u1eebng lo\u1ea1i da?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 n\u1eb1m \u1edf ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 SPF hay PA m\u00e0 c\u00f2n ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o lo\u1ea1i da c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch ch\u1ecdn <\/span><b>kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng cho c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i da<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4228\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4228\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4228\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/75-2.webp\" alt=\"L\u00e0m sao \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u1eebng lo\u1ea1i da\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/75-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/75-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/75-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/75-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4228\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">L\u00e0m sao \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u1eebng lo\u1ea1i da<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"da-nhay-cam\"><\/span><b><i>Da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m<\/i><\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0n da d\u1ec5 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u0103m s\u00f3c nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng v\u00e0 c\u1ea9n tr\u1ecdng. V\u1edbi lo\u1ea1i da n\u00e0y, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean \u01b0u ti\u00ean <\/span>kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u1eadt l\u00fd ch\u1ee9a Titanium Dioxide v\u00e0 Zinc Oxide \u2013 nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1o l\u1edbp m\u00e0ng ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 tia UV ngay khi ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac.<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfu ph\u1ea3i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc, h\u00e3y th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf m\u1ed9t v\u00f9ng da nh\u1ecf nh\u01b0 d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1eb1m ho\u1eb7c sau tai \u0111\u1ec3 xem ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng. Tr\u00e1nh xa c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ee9a h\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u1ec7u, c\u1ed3n kh\u00f4 ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ea5t b\u1ea3o qu\u1ea3n m\u1ea1nh.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"da-kho\"><\/span><b><i>Da kh\u00f4<\/i><\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ai c\u00f3 l\u00e0n da kh\u00f4, n\u00ean t\u00ecm \u0111\u1ebfn <\/span>kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng t\u00edch h\u1ee3p kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m. H\u00e3y ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9a hyaluronic acid, glycerin ho\u1eb7c ceramide, gi\u00fap gi\u1eef n\u01b0\u1edbc, tr\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m v\u00e0 l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da.<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem c\u00f3 c\u1ed3n ho\u1eb7c h\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u1ec7u m\u1ea1nh v\u00ec ch\u00fang c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn da th\u00eam kh\u00f4 r\u00e1p, d\u1ec5 bong tr\u00f3c v\u00e0 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng. Lu\u00f4n k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u00f4i ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"da-dau\"><\/span><b><i>Da d\u1ea7u<\/i><\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>\u0110\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a da d\u1ea7u l\u00e0 ti\u1ebft nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn, d\u1ec5 g\u00e2y b\u00ed b\u00e1ch v\u00e0 n\u1ed5i m\u1ee5n n\u1ebfu ch\u1ecdn sai s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m. V\u1edbi lo\u1ea1i da n\u00e0y, n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc d\u1ea1ng gel ho\u1eb7c lotion m\u1ecfng nh\u1eb9, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9a d\u1ea7u (oil-free), kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n (non-comedogenic), th\u1ea5m nhanh v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i m\u00e0ng tr\u1eafng tr\u00ean da.<\/p>\n<p>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 lo\u1ea1i kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng cho c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i da d\u1ea7u c\u00f2n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ki\u1ec1m d\u1ea7u, gi\u00fap b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da kh\u00f4 tho\u00e1ng v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu su\u1ed1t ng\u00e0y d\u00e0i.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"nhung-nguyen-tac-can-nho-khi-su-dung-kem-chong-nang\"><\/span><b>Nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc c\u1ea7n nh\u1edb khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u00f9 b\u1ea1n thu\u1ed9c lo\u1ea1i da n\u00e0o, vi\u1ec7c d\u00f9ng \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea1n n\u00ean l\u01b0u \u00fd:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4229\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4229\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4229\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/75-3.webp\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc c\u1ea7n nh\u1edb khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/75-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/75-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/75-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/75-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4229\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc c\u1ea7n nh\u1edb khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m cho \u0111\u00fang v\u00f9ng da: Da m\u1eb7t m\u1ecfng v\u00e0 nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m h\u01a1n da body, n\u00ean \u0111\u1eebng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng to\u00e0n th\u00e2n cho v\u00f9ng m\u1eb7t v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u01afu ti\u00ean ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 SPF t\u1eeb 30\u201350 v\u00e0 PA+++ tr\u1edf l\u00ean: \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ee9c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng cho \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n kh\u00ed h\u1eadu n\u00f3ng \u1ea9m nh\u01b0 \u1edf Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Thoa kem tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ra ngo\u00e0i \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 20 ph\u00fat: Gi\u00fap kem c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1eddi gian t\u1ea1o l\u1edbp m\u00e0ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7, tr\u00e1nh hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u201cch\u00e1y n\u1eafng s\u1edbm\u201d.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u00f4i l\u1ea1i sau m\u1ed7i 2 gi\u1edd n\u1ebfu ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi ho\u1eb7c sau khi ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc, m\u1ed3 h\u00f4i.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00e1c bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p che ch\u1eafn kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 \u00e1o kho\u00e1c, kh\u1ea9u trang, k\u00ednh r\u00e2m, ho\u1eb7c vi\u00ean u\u1ed1ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1ea9y trang cu\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y: D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng trang \u0111i\u1ec3m, l\u1edbp kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh g\u00e2y b\u00edt t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"loi-khuyen-khi-lua-chon-kem-chong-nang-tren-thi-truong\"><\/span><b>L\u1eddi khuy\u00ean khi l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Lu\u00f4n ki\u1ec3m tra b\u1ea3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n: Tr\u00e1nh xa c\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi lo\u1ea1i da c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ecdn th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u uy t\u00edn, c\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng: Gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 an to\u00e0n khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng l\u00e2u d\u00e0i.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi d\u00f9ng to\u00e0n m\u1eb7t: V\u1edbi da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng kh\u00f4ng mong mu\u1ed1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4230\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4230\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4230\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/75-4.webp\" alt=\"L\u1eddi khuy\u00ean khi l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/75-4.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/75-4-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/75-4-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/75-4-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4230\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">L\u1eddi khuy\u00ean khi l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tong-ket\"><\/span><b>T\u1ed5ng k\u1ebft<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Hy v\u1ecdng qua b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y, b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn <\/span><b>kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng cho c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i da<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c. \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 th\u00f4ng minh cho t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai l\u00e0n da c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n!<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u c\u00e1ch nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft v\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng cho c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i da m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, an to\u00e0n v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":4231,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4226","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-thong-tin-nganh"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4226","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4226"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4226\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4233,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4226\/revisions\/4233"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4231"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4226"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=4226"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=4226"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}